senpai anymore...

Even though it was just once, I ended up having sex with
Hayamichi-senpai.

promise...

With this, everything will be as if it never happened...
Yes...
Something like that... never again...

As I think that, the memories of that time we had sex keep
crossing my mind...
Every time, my private parts would throb and heat up...
.........I end up comforting myself.
